      </p>
      <p class="mt-2">
        Built with <a href="https://astro.build" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Astro</a> 
        {' '}and deployed on <a href="https://pages.github.com" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">GitHub Pages</a>
      </p>
    </div>
